She doesn't have
that many friends.

297
00:22:51.065 --> 00:22:53.415
I've talked to all the ones
that I know.

298
00:22:53.459 --> 00:22:57.288
-Boyfriend?
-Chris hasn't seen her.

299
00:22:57.376 --> 00:22:59.247
[Amy] And he seems
like a pretty nice guy.

300
00:22:59.290 --> 00:23:01.379
Chris who? You got a number?

