1159
01:21:14.434 --> 01:21:15.739
[Don] Sarah!

1160
01:21:22.615 --> 01:21:23.878
Sarah!

1161
01:21:25.489 --> 01:21:27.056
I need help.

1162
01:21:34.236 --> 01:21:36.587
Sir? Sir?

1163
01:21:40.982 --> 01:21:42.636
